	* Release 0.03.
	* New function: encoded_header_len.
	* body_encode()/header_encode(): fallback to US-ASCII if possible.
	* Documentation: definitions of ``charset'' & ``encoding''.
	* Typos on Encode::FB_*.
	* More test cases.

